  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    direction TB\n\n    init_db: Initialize or Load Logs DB\n    start_rpc_log_fetch: Use RPC to fetch Logs\n    start_fast_log_fetch: Use P2P network to fetch batch logs\n\n    state if_close_to_head <<choice>>\n\n    [*] --> init_db: startup\n\n    init_db --> if_close_to_head: Calculate Logs Diff\n    if_close_to_head --> start_rpc_log_fetch: close to chain head (configurable) or fast sync disabled (configurable)\n    if_close_to_head --> start_fast_log_fetch: not close to chain head (configurable)\n    start_fast_log_fetch --> start_rpc_log_fetch: get logs batch\n\n    start_rpc_log_fetch --> [*]: system shutdown\n    start_fast_log_fetch --> [*]: system shutdown\n\n",
  "diagram_type": "state size:600..900",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T04:32:49.474055",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个日志同步的状态图。系统启动后，首先要初始化或者加载本地的日志数据库，然后根据当前节点距离链头的远近来决定走哪条路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "init_db",
        "startup",
        "if_close_to_head"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是startup事件触发init_db，然后计算日志差异后进入一个判断节点。这个判断条件具体是什么？是距离链头是否接近吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "init_db",
        "Calculate Logs Diff",
        "if_close_to_head"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，判断条件是\"if close to head\"。如果接近链头，或者用户配置了禁用快速同步，就走RPC逐条拉取日志；如果不接近链头，就用P2P网络批量获取。这两个都是可配置的阈值。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "if_close_to_head",
        "start_rpc_log_fetch",
        "start_fast_log_fetch",
        "configurable"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主分支画出来。起点到init_db，然后到判断节点，分出两条路：一条到RPC日志获取，一条到P2P批量获取。两条路最终都应该能正常结束吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "start_rpc_log_fetch",
        "start_fast_log_fetch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，P2P批量获取之后还需要一个步骤——拿到一批日志后，最终还是要转到RPC方式去获取剩余的日志。所以start_fast_log_fetch后面要连到start_rpc_log_fetch，触发条件是\"get logs batch\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "start_fast_log_fetch",
        "start_rpc_log_fetch",
        "get logs batch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以快速同步只是第一阶段，批量拉完之后还是要切到RPC模式继续同步。那两种获取方式的终止状态都是系统关闭吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "start_rpc_log_fetch",
        "start_fast_log_fetch",
        "system shutdown"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，无论是RPC直接启动，还是P2P转RPC，最终正常结束都是system shutdown。另外注意判断节点的两条分支标注要写清楚：接近链头或禁用快速同步走RPC，不接近链头才走P2P。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "if_close_to_head",
        "close to chain head (configurable)",
        "fast sync disabled (configurable)",
        "not close to chain head (configurable)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。整个流程是：startup触发数据库初始化，计算日志差异后根据距离链头的远近和配置选择同步策略，P2P批量获取后转RPC继续，最终系统关闭。方向我设为TB纵向布局，结构应该清晰了。",
